This is a dev texture map I made to have tournaments on and I've tested it with bots and it was quite fun.
it features to bases and a large bridge type structure in the middle for sniper but that's if you can get up there without being killed. this download also includes the nav files so you don't have to create one and constructive criticism would be helpful for future releases. heres a video with bots lol
